## 🧹 DRY 2: Brew candidates block duplicated verbatim in `.zshrc` and `.bashrc`

The ~20-line `brew_candidates` loop is copy-pasted identically in both skel shell files.

**Fix:**
- Extract to `skel/default/.config/brew-init.sh`
- Both `.zshrc` and `.bashrc` source it: `[[ -f "${HOME}/.config/brew-init.sh" ]] && source "${HOME}/.config/brew-init.sh"`
- Deployed automatically via the existing `.config` dir merge — no installer changes needed
- `scripts/lib/brew-env.sh` serves a different purpose (non-interactive script context) and stays as-is

**Files:** `skel/default/.zshrc`, `skel/default/.bashrc`, `skel/default/.config/brew-init.sh` (new)

